cyrus-sasl-oauth2-oidc (1.0.0-1) trixie; urgency=medium

  * Initial Debian package release
  * OAuth2/OIDC SASL plugin for Cyrus SASL
  * Support for Bearer token authentication
  * OpenID Connect ID token validation
  * JWT token introspection capabilities
  * Multiple issuer and audience support
  * Compatible with Debian Trixie

 -- Stephane Benoit <stefb@wizzz.net>  Mon, 12 Aug 2025 19:16:46 +0200
